  <title>Showing the Mistake Counter</title>

  <media its:translate="no" type="image" src="figures/error_counter.png">
    <p>Mistake Counter</p>
  </media>

  <p><app>Hexkudo</app> can display a counter that shows the number of mistakes.</p>

  <p>Because you can mistakenly select the wrong cell, <app>Hexkudo</app> gives you three seconds to correct your error before recording the mistake.</p>

  <p>You can hide or show the counter:</p>

  <steps>
    <item><p>Click the menu button (<media its:translate="no" type="image" src="figures/open-menu-symbolic.svg"/>).</p></item>
    <item><p>Go to <gui style="menuitem">Preferences</gui>.</p></item>
    <item><p>In the <gui style="group">General</gui> section, select the <gui style="button">Show Mistake Counter</gui> checkbox.</p></item>
  </steps>
